Global Air Anesthesia Machine Market Insights
Air Anesthesia Machine Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Air Anesthesia Machine Market Overview
The global air anesthesia machine market is experiencing robust growth due to rising demand for anesthesia equipment across hospitals, surgical centers, and clinics. The market value is expected to reach USD 2.2 billion by 2026, growing at a CAGR of 6.3% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by technological advancements, increasing surgical procedures, and an expanding geriatric population requiring anesthesia for various medical treatments. As healthcare infrastructure improves, the demand for efficient and reliable anesthesia machines continues to rise globally, fueling the market expansion.

